    id:"en4", category:"Entertainment", categorySlug:"entertainment",
    headline:"Davido and Wizkid End Decade-Long Rivalry With Historic Joint Album Announcement",
    snippet:"Nigeria's two biggest music stars announced a collaborative album — 'Lagos to the World' — due in June, accompanied by a joint world tour. The announcement crashed streaming platforms.",
